<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:08:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>过去战争的惨痛教训为以色列与哈马斯战争的战斗提供了信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/bitter-lessons-of-past-wars-inform-fighting-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-8ccd-d7a8-afcf-aeeff4a40000</link><description>以色列南方司令部认为，哈马斯更愿意派遣小股部队，用反坦克导弹、迫击炮和狙击手火力打击以色列军队。由于加沙地带兵力密集，误伤是一个问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:51:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/bitter-lessons-of-past-wars-inform-fighting-in-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-8ccd-d7a8-afcf-aeeff4a40000</guid></item><item><title>由于司法部长莱文拒绝召开司法任命委员会，退休法官将填补以色列法院的空缺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-judges-to-fill-vacancies-as-justice-minister-refuses-to-convene-panel/0000018b-9083-d477-a1ff-f78361740000</link><description>此举得到了最高法院代院长乌兹·沃格尔曼的同意，为任命 14 名退休法官铺平了道路</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/retired-israeli-judges-to-fill-vacancies-as-justice-minister-refuses-to-convene-panel/0000018b-9083-d477-a1ff-f78361740000</guid></item><item><title>安吉丽娜·朱莉猛烈抨击以色列在加沙“蓄意轰炸被困人口”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/angelina-jolie-slams-israels-deliberate-bombing-of-trapped-population-in-gaza/0000018b-9021-d477-a1ff-f721c9ec0000</link><description>朱莉在 Instagram 上发帖，谴责以色列对“儿童、妇女和家庭”进行“蓄意轰炸”，这些儿童、妇女和家庭在以色列与哈马斯的战争中“被剥夺了食物、药品和人道主义援助，违反了国际法”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/angelina-jolie-slams-israels-deliberate-bombing-of-trapped-population-in-gaza/0000018b-9021-d477-a1ff-f721c9ec0000</guid></item><item><title>全球左派对 10 月 7 日的反应威胁到反占领的斗争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-global-lefts-reaction-to-october-7-threatens-the-fight-against-the-occupation/0000018b-8b8d-d7a8-afcf-abaf5d670000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:18:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-global-lefts-reaction-to-october-7-threatens-the-fight-against-the-occupation/0000018b-8b8d-d7a8-afcf-abaf5d670000</guid></item><item><title>艾哈迈德希望以色列人倾听加沙人的声音。随后他的23名家人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ahmed-wanted-israelis-to-listen-to-gazans-then-23-of-his-family-members-were-killed/0000018b-8fb6-db7e-af9b-eff7d71f0000</link><description>在 Facebook 页面“跨越墙”上，以色列人用希伯来语阅读加沙人的个人故事，直到最后更新：“该页面创始人的整个家庭都被炸死了。”该页面的以色列联合创始人现在表示：“我不知道我们是否能够再次建造那座桥”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ahmed-wanted-israelis-to-listen-to-gazans-then-23-of-his-family-members-were-killed/0000018b-8fb6-db7e-af9b-eff7d71f0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的另一个受害者：基布兹的美术馆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-kibbutzs-art-gallery-became-another-victim-of-hamas/0000018b-3dcf-d2b8-a7db-fdefbb4a0000</link><description>在哈马斯摧毁贝埃里基布兹的过程中，恐怖分子还袭击了馆长索菲·贝尔宗·麦基及其家人。他们幸存下来，但基布兹的画廊被烧毁</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 13:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-kibbutzs-art-gallery-became-another-victim-of-hamas/0000018b-3dcf-d2b8-a7db-fdefbb4a0000</guid></item><item><title>互动地图描绘了哈马斯 10 月 7 日在以色列和加沙边境社区所犯下的暴行规模</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/interactive-map-depicts-scale-of-hamas-oct-7-atrocities-on-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-8fcf-d7a8-afcf-afef4f600000</link><description>新网站“绘制大屠杀地图”允许用户点击每个受影响的以色列城镇并阅读那里发生的事情的摘要。单独的、颜色编码的点突出显示了被杀害或绑架的以色列人的位置</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 13:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/interactive-map-depicts-scale-of-hamas-oct-7-atrocities-on-israeli-gaza-border-communities/0000018b-8fcf-d7a8-afcf-afef4f600000</guid></item><item><title>随着愤怒的加剧，加沙人质的家人发誓不会给予以色列政府“无限的信任”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/as-anger-grows-families-of-gaza-hostages-vow-not-to-give-israeli-govt-endless-credit/0000018b-8fb5-d477-a1ff-ffb51a020000</link><description>家属发言人表示，“家属们感到不安，因为他们感觉没有就释放人质问题进行认真的谈判”。 “如果事情继续这样下去，我们别无选择，只能加大力度”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 12:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/as-anger-grows-families-of-gaza-hostages-vow-not-to-give-israeli-govt-endless-credit/0000018b-8fb5-d477-a1ff-ffb51a020000</guid></item><item><title>在鱼雷和潜艇之间：哈马斯展示无人攻击武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/between-a-torpedo-and-a-submarine-hamas-reveals-unmanned-attack-weapon/0000018b-8f2f-db71-a7df-ffeffda80000</link><description>专家分析了无人水面车辆的视频后得出结论，它缺乏先进的功能。它有一个重达数十公斤的战斗头和一个不允许瞄准移动物体的GPS制导系统</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 12:39:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/between-a-torpedo-and-a-submarine-hamas-reveals-unmanned-attack-weapon/0000018b-8f2f-db71-a7df-ffeffda80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队计划招募没有以色列国防军经验的定居者来保卫极端正统的西岸定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements/0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000</link><description>新兵预计将接受为期三周的加速基础训练，之后他们将武装起来并驻扎在定居点。该计划向 27 岁至 50 岁、未曾在以色列军队服役的平民开放</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 11:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-to-recruit-settlers-with-no-army-experience-to-guard-west-bank-settlements/0000018b-8f63-d7a8-afcf-afe3a9b00000</guid></item><item><title>德国正式取缔哈马斯，解散庆祝 10 月 7 日大屠杀的组织 Samidoun</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/germany-officially-outlaws-hamas-disbands-samidoun-group-that-celebrated-oct-7-massacre/0000018b-8f95-d7a8-afcf-afb749e90000</link><description>德国最高安全官员在宣布禁令的声明中表示，“在德国举行自发的‘庆祝活动’，以回应哈马斯对以色列的可怕恐怖袭击，显示了萨米敦的反犹太主义、不人道的世界观”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 11:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/germany-officially-outlaws-hamas-disbands-samidoun-group-that-celebrated-oct-7-massacre/0000018b-8f95-d7a8-afcf-afb749e90000</guid></item><item><title>检查站、商店关门、药品不足：哈原已成为一座鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/checkpoints-closed-shops-not-enough-medicine-hawara-has-become-a-ghost-town/0000018b-8abc-dce3-afaf-affe3c450000</link><description>以色列军方设置了路障，将约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦城镇一分为二，使人们难以移动或到达周围社区。由于担心定居者的袭击，居民们在离开家时三思而后行。军方表示已命令部队允许自由行人通行</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 10:52:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/checkpoints-closed-shops-not-enough-medicine-hawara-has-become-a-ghost-town/0000018b-8abc-dce3-afaf-affe3c450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府担心卡塔尔人质调解受到损害，不阻止半岛电视台关闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-prevents-al-jazeera-shut-down-fearing-harm-to-qatari-hostage-mediation/0000018b-8f0e-d728-a9ab-dfde4aff0000</link><description>以色列内阁批准了紧急法规，允许政府关闭安全官员认为危害国家安全的媒体渠道，但通讯部长和司法部长均表示，决定权在国防部长约阿夫·加兰特手中</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 08:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-prevents-al-jazeera-shut-down-fearing-harm-to-qatari-hostage-mediation/0000018b-8f0e-d728-a9ab-dfde4aff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列，当心：在战争中，末日犹太极端民族主义者处于狂喜状态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-beware-nationalist-haredis-are-in-a-state-of-ecstasy/0000018b-8c23-d7a8-afcf-aea34fd90000</link><description>他们的眼睛闪闪发光。他们谈论“第二次灾难”。他们相信这是弥赛亚的时代。对于极端正统民族主义者来说，与哈马斯的战争是一个双重幻想：犹太人对大以色列的全面统治，以及从当今自由民主以色列的废墟中诞生的原教旨主义犹太人</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 07:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-beware-nationalist-haredis-are-in-a-state-of-ecstasy/0000018b-8c23-d7a8-afcf-aea34fd90000</guid></item><item><title>火箭直接袭击以色列北部和中部；内塔尼亚胡：“没有什么能阻止我们”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-in-lebanon-after-missile-launch-hamas-commander-killed-in-idf-airstrike/0000018b-8e75-db7e-af9b-eff7619c0000</link><description>18 名以色列士兵和军官在加沙地面进攻中丧生 ■ 哈马斯：195 名巴勒斯坦人在以色列对贾巴利亚难民营的袭击中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军在导弹发射后对黎巴嫩发动空袭 ■ 以色列空袭杀死了哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官、巴勒斯坦民族权力机构领导人之一易卜拉欣·比亚里10 月 7 日大屠杀 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：超过 9,000 名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 242 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 05:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/idf-strikes-in-lebanon-after-missile-launch-hamas-commander-killed-in-idf-airstrike/0000018b-8e75-db7e-af9b-eff7619c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列寻求国际合法性，但时间已经不多了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-seeks-international-legitimacy-but-time-is-running-out/0000018b-8ca8-d46b-a18f-8cf906bf0000</link><description>尽管哈马斯的杀人意图显而易见，但国际合法性的时钟正在滴答作响，以色列对黑色星